RACE.RACE_TEXT: CHARLES TOWN RACE 4 6 1/2F Dirt CR: 66. Claiming Purse 19400. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES. Weight, 124 lbs. FORT ZANNA rounded the first turn about the five path, picked up the chase past the three eighths pole and raced in the five path of the far turn.

SHINY PENNY rounded the first turn in the four path, gave chase leaving the seven sixteenths pole but flattened in the five path of the far turn.
